<div class="page-header">
  <h1>h-card as a service</h1>
</div>

<p class="alert alert-danger">
  This is just a prototype to test out an idea.
  This website will not stay at this domain forever.
  <b>Do not expect its URLs to last.</b>
</p>

<p class="alert alert-danger">
  ALL information entered into this site is publicly visible by anyone. 
  Don't add any information that you want to keep private.
</p>

<p class="alert alert-info">
  The code that powers this site can be found on GitHub at:
  <b><%= link_to "github.com/veganstraightedge/h-card-as-a-service", "https://github.com/veganstraightedge/h-card-as-a-service" %></b>.<br>
  Feel free to fork it, submit issues, send pull requests or
  <b><a href="https://heroku.com/deploy?template=https://github.com/veganstraightedge/h-card-as-a-service">deploy it to Heroku</a>.</b>
</p>

<%= form_tag new_path, method: :get, html: {class: "form"} do %>
  <%= label_tag :website do %>
    To get started, <br />
    Type the URL of your personal website
  <% end %>
  <%= url_field_tag :website, nil, placeholder: "http://example.com", class: "form-control input-lg" %>
  <div class="actions">
    <button class="btn btn-success btn-lg">Get started...</button>
  </div>
<% end %>
